[gd_scene load_steps=14 format=3 uid="uid://b0embergrave_s1room02_wide_chunk"]

; S1 bigger-rooms retrofit Stage 1A (ticket 86ca3kpzz). Hand-widened proof
; chunk: 30x8 tiles = 960x256 px (vs the 15x8 / 480x256 single-screen chunks).
; Drives the camera-scroll machinery: with world bounds wider than the
; viewport, CameraDirector.set_world_bounds takes the SCROLL branch (not the
; centre branch) so the camera follows the player across the wider floor.
; Reuses the S1CloisterChunk painter (grid_w=30 override) + the warm flat
; floor PNG absorbed from PR #403. Wall collision perimeter + seams + props
; redistributed across the wider span. ONE proof chunk only (OOS: widening all
; 8 rooms / procgen — see ticket).

